metadata.title: Seabird Colonies for PWS
metadata.description: Data Type: Birds;  This layer contains seabird colony data for Prince William Sound. The US Fish and Wildlife Service (USFWS) publishes the seabird colony data which is based on the 1978 "Alaska Seabird Colonies Catalog" computer database and unpublished archives containing updates subsequent to the 1989 Exxon Valdez oil spill.
